Therefore, it is likely to belong to the database (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of text descriptors and image analysis, which suggests that it may also belong to the information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), and computer vision (cs.CV) sub-categories.
